Let's get inking!

I beat Link’s Awakening last night! For the most part it was just as enjoyable as the original 1993 version that was my first 2D Zelda. Though I wouldn’t want it to return, the art style was charming and I did like it! Unfortunately, I do think more new features should have been added. Chamber Dungeons were a let down and figure collecting was pointless. The quality of life improvements were appreciated and I was grateful for more heart containers and seashells to hunt down and add to my total playtime. Most of the music was fantastic, with the tragic exception of Manbo’s Manbo which was hugely downgraded. Still I hope they release a soundtrack! $60 seems a bit unfair after everything is said and done, but I’m going to support the series I love best, regardless, in hopes of more remakes in the future. Also this game needs d-pad support 😑 #loz

caption.text: BOWSER STARRING @jyn_17  @calikko #mariobros #marioparty #bowser #bowserjr #videogames #nintendo #nintendoswitch #nes #hiphoplately #hotnewhiphopdaily #princesspeach #toadstool #luigi #luigismansion #asaprocky #dababychallenge #dababy #intro

It’s finally Fall!! 🍁🍂 Monday was the official start to autumn, even if it doesn’t feel like it yet.
.
For me, fall is the best season for a lot of reasons, one being that it reminds me of one of my favorite genres of games - farming. I grew up playing Harvest Moon games, but the Switch introduced me to Stardew Valley, which is hands down the best farming simulation game to date.
.
There are a lot of great farming themed board games, but one of the classics in my book is Agricola. This worker placement game has you start small and build up crops and livestock, all while growing your family and keeping them fed. It requires some clever strategy and is a lot of fun!
.
Another fall staple I love is apple pie. I use Grandma Ople’s apple pie recipe, which you can find on google. One thing I really like about it is that it doesn’t use any cinnamon, but you can add some if you’re into that! I also love that the lattice top allows you the freedom to be creative with how your pie looks. I attempted a D20 outline with my pie, but if you see a triforce, that’s okay too 😜
.
Enough simulated farming and you just might get a bug for the real thing! I made this cute dice planter from a cheap terra-cotta pot from Hobby Lobby. Just a couple coats of white spray paint and black acrylic dots and you’ve got a cool DIY place for your real life plants too 🌱
.
What’s your favorite thing about fall?
.

preview_comments.text: @simo_tankabbestia triste pensare che i cabinati di Outrun disponibili una volta nelle nostre sale giochi, oggi saranno tra la polvere di qualche cantina o blindati nella casa di qualche appassionato.

caption.text:
CONDIVIDI NELLE STORIE ⬇️ Tra i capostipite di un genere fortunato, Outrun gettò le basi per il solco arcade dei giochi di corse. Oggi si ricorda la prima uscita in cabinato, ma siamo sicuri che in casa avete almeno una console sul quale giocarlo. L’impatto di Outrun è stato tale che nel corso dei decenni non si è mai smesso di riproporlo. Occorre però tenere a mente che la versione più appagante rimane quella per cabinato. O meglio, per cabinati, dal momento che esistono diverse versioni dalle peculiarità esclusive. Yu Suzuki - che conoscete per Shenmue - ha progettato Outrun in modo tale che possano essere aggiunti effetti motori, come vibrazioni, responso virtuale dello sterzo, o inclinazioni del sedile di gioco, senza alterarne la formula. Così, tra gli anni ’80 e ’90, troviamo le sale giochi popolate da tre versioni di Outrun, tra le quali una fatta per il gioco in piedi (“Upright”) dotata di suddetto force feedback. Potete recuperare Outrun su PC, Nintendo 3DS, Switch e console datate di SEGA e Commodore.

Commenta con la tua opinione, tagga un amico e condividi. Inoltre, unisciti al gruppo Telegram di Gamerversum. Essa é pra quem curte Fortnite!
No blog oficial da Epic Games, a equipe de Fortnite anunciou que a nova atualização do jogo trará mudanças significativas ao seu sistema de matchmaking, onde jogadores com o mesmo nível de habilidade se juntarão em uma mesma partida.
"Na atualização v10.40, estamos introduzindo uma lógica melhorada de matchmaking aos modos centrais de Battle Royale para criar partidas mais justas", diz a mensagem. "O que isso quer dizer? Você terá mais chances de se juntar a jogadores de habilidade similar, e quando seu jogo melhorar, seus oponentes também. Vamos lançar isso lentamente para todas as regiões nos modos de Battle Royale enquanto testamos e monitoramos o desempenho disso. Estamos animados para disponibilizar isso para todos jogarem e vamos continuar a atualizar o sistema."
Outra coisa legal é que a Epic revelou que a Temporada 11 receberá bots!
Que servirão para ajudar os jogadores a treinarem suas habilidades e irem evoluindo dentro do game.
"Eles se comportarão de forma similar a jogadores normais e ajudarão a criar um caminho melhor para usuários melhorarem suas habilidades", explicam. "Bots funcionarão em conjunto com o novo sistema de matchmaking, e quando suas habilidades melhorarem, você enfrentará menos bots." #fortnite #epicgames #battleroyale #temporada11 #matchmaking #news #fortnitenews #ps4 #ps4pro #ps4slim #xbox #xboxone #xboxones #xboxonex #nintendo #nintendoswitch #pc #pcgamer #gamer #games #gamesonline #nitrogames

caption.text: had to re-upload this, the last one was all janked up.. fun little kaizo level with more than just shell tech, very enjoyable ☺️

Gulpin and Swalot’s Picnic Day!

I figured illustrating these guys at a picnic would suit them, and be a little bit more interesting than just drawing them by themselves. They are known to be big eaters after all! Luckily they are showing their manners and taking their time, rather than swallowing entire watermelons whole. 
These guys were one of the winners of one of my patreon exclusive Pokepolls! Each Monday I post a poll for the week between three Pokémon. At the end of the week the winner will get an illustration with their full evolutionary line! This weeks vote is between Lillipup, Snorunt, and Remoraid. If you want to cast a vote you’ve just got to pick the Accelerator tier or higher! :) and thank you to my current patron for your continued support and votes! .
